Marks & Spencer - Wikipedia






















 






Marks & Spencer

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"M&S" redirects here. This article is about the department store. For other uses, see M&S (disambiguation).

Marks & Spencer plc





Type

